init_text: All of the "#1 Dad" mugs in the world change to show the actual ranking of Dads suddenly.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: He's not on the list at all.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: Oh my God, this is horrible.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: I quickly scour the list to see if there is any other name that looks like my dad's.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: I ask her if my dad is really my biological father.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: She's very confused and asks me why I would even ask such a thing.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: She tells me that it must be some kind of mistake.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: She tells me that I should just ignore the mug.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: I decide to just go ask my dad about it in person.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: I get to his office at the university and ask him about the mug.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: But I pull out the mug and show it to him.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: He doesn't know what to say.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: I ask why he wouldn't trust my mom.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: He says that there's no other explanation that makes sense.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: He says that if my mom cheated on him, then she probably had an affair with my biological father.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: She says that she doesn't know what to do or say.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: But I am not interested in hearing it.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: I just want to be done with this woman.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: I ask how she could have done this to my father.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: I will never speak to her again.
